---
import Layout from '@/components/chrome/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = '2026-05-07';
---
<Layout
  title="Affiliate Disclosures — strguests.tools"
  description="How strguests.tools uses affiliate links and the relationships behind any tool we recommend."
  path="/disclosures"
>
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 py-12 prose">
    <header>
      <p class="label text-[color:var(--accent-700)]">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="mt-2 font-serif text-h1 text-navy">
        Affiliate Disclosures<span class="period-accent">.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-small text-ink-3 font-mono">Last updated <time datetime={lastUpdated}>{lastUpdated}</time></p>
    </header>

    <section class="mt-9">
      <p class="text-ui text-graphite leading-relaxed">
        strguests.tools is a free site supported in part by affiliate revenue. When we link to a
        third-party tool (guidebook software, design tools, printing services), some of those
        links pay us a commission if you sign up or buy. <strong>This never costs you extra</strong>,
        and it doesn't change which tools we recommend.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-9">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-h2 text-navy">Our recommendation rule</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-ui text-graphite leading-relaxed">
        We only recommend tools we'd happily use ourselves on a real listing. If a tool is the
        right fit but doesn't have an affiliate program, we still link to it (just plain). If a
        tool offers a generous commission but we don't think it's the best option, we don't
        recommend it.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-9">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-h2 text-navy">Categories with affiliate relationships</h2>
      <ul class="mt-3 ml-6 list-disc text-ui text-graphite space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Digital guidebook software</strong> — Touch Stay, Hostfully Guidebook, YourWelcome</li>
        <li><strong>Design tools</strong> — Canva Pro</li>
        <li><strong>Print services</strong> — Printful, Printify (planned)</li>
        <li><strong>Sister product</strong> — <a class="text-[color:var(--accent-700)]" href="https://thestrledger.com">The STR Ledger</a> (Excel templates) is operated by the same team — purchases there fund this free site.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-9">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-h2 text-navy">FTC compliance</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-ui text-graphite leading-relaxed">
        Per the U.S. Federal Trade Commission's endorsement guidelines, this disclosure is
        intended to make our material connection to the products above clear. If you spot an
        affiliated link that isn't visibly tagged on a content page, please email us — we'll fix
        the labeling.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-9">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-h2 text-navy">Contact</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-ui text-graphite leading-relaxed">
        Questions about a specific recommendation:
        <a class="text-[color:var(--accent-700)]" href="mailto:hello@strguests.tools">hello@strguests.tools</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>
